<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>500 Internal Server Error</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #f4f4f4;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			color: #333;
			text-align: center;
			padding: 50px;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 3em;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		p {
			font-size: 1.5em;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		a {
			color: #333;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		a:hover {
			color: #666;
		}

		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.image {
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		/* Media queries */
		@media (max-width: 767px) {
			h1 {
				font-size: 2em;
			}

			p {
				font-size: 1.2em;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<img src="https://www.example.com/images/500-error.png" alt="" class="image">
		<h1>500 Internal Server Error</h1>
		<p>Sorry, something went wrong on our end. We are working to fix the issue.</p>
		<p>Please check back later or return to the <a href="/home">homepage</a>.</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
